text: Fyter Fest (2021) was a two-part professional wrestling show made by All Elite Wrestling (AEW). It took place on July 14 and July 21, 2021. The first week was held at the H-E-B Center at Cedar Park in Cedar Park, Texas and the second week was held at the Curtis Culwell Center in Garland, Texas. Both nights were aired as special episodes of Dynamite. It was the third Fyter Fest event held by AEW. Week 1's main event saw Darby Allin defeat Ethan Page in a Coffin match.
